Date: 1998-11-09

Title: Wick Rotation and Abelian Bosonization

Authors: Aleksandar Bogojevic (Institute of Physics, Belgrade) and Olivera

Miskovic (Vinca Institute)Comments: 8 pages, Latex 2e, 3 figures

We investigate the connection between Abelian bosonization in the Minkowskiand Euclidean formalisms. The relation is best seen in the complex timeformalism of S. A. Fulling and S. N. M. Ruijsenaars \cite{fulling}.